Cats in the summer: Shade is important to keep cool🍧

Summer heat can be dangerous, not just for us but for our furry companions too. 🌡️☀️
Always make sure your pets have access to cool, shaded areas, especially during peak sun hours. Shade isn’t just comfort it’s protection from overheating, heatstroke, and paw burns.
Let’s keep our animals safe, hydrated, and cool this summer. 🐾❤️

💚FUNFACT💚

🐾 TAHUKAH ANDA❓

Kucing sebenarnya boleh berenang secara semula jadI❗️ Tapi… banyak je yang “manja air” 🫣 nampak air terus lari❗️😹💦

✍🏼Tapi ada juga beberapa baka kucing yang memang suka air, contohnya:

1️⃣ Turkish Van 👉🏼 digelar kucing berenang sebab memang suka mandi & main air.
2️⃣ Bengal 👉🏼 aktif & berani, langsung tak kisah basah.
3️⃣ Maine Coon 👉🏼 bulu mereka sedikit kalis air & suka aktiviti luar.🌊🐱

Kalau ada salah satu baka ni, mungkin anda dah biasa nampak mereka ‘terjun tiruk’ dalam air❗️😆

node.text:
Most pet parents are told their dog or cat has allergies, inflammation, or chronic yeast — but no one explains why it keeps coming back.
⁠
The truth is, detox has to go in the right order. You can’t skip to the supplements without preparing the body first.⁠
⁠
Here’s the exact step-by-step method I use with my own pets and every client:⁠

➊ Open the drainage pathways⁠
